  "title": "Customer Service Executive (Import and Export)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>In charge of preparation and processing of sales order and handling of documentations</li>\n  <li>Responsible ensuring the accuracy in documents and emails as well as preventing errors and maintaining smooth operations</li>\n  <li>In charge of following up on the status of sales orders, payment checks as well as liaison with the relevant departments and organisation </li>\n  <li>Responsible in supporting teamwork and assist with ad-hoc task</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirement:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum Diploma in Business Adminstration or relevant</li>\n  <li>Minimum 2 years of working experience in sales support / customer service with knowledge of shipping terms and export documentation</li>\n  <li>Letter of Credit knowledge will be a advantage</li>\n</ul>\n<p>To submit your application, please apply online to <a href=\"mailto:apply@rn-care.com\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>apply@rn-care.com </strong></a>or call +(65) <a href=\"tel:6513 5697\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>6513 5697</strong></a> for private and confidential discussion.</p>\n<p>Your interest will be treated with the strictest of confidence. We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified or contacted.</p>\n<p><strong>RN Care Pte. Ltd</strong><br>\n<strong>EA License No: 17C8900</strong></p>",
